sequenceDiagram
  participant Client as MCP Client
  participant Gateway as MCP API Gateway
  participant Mcp as ceo-chat-mcp
  participant Core as ceo-chat-core
  participant Db as PostgreSQL

  Client->>Gateway: POST /mcp
  Gateway->>Mcp: Forward authenticated request
  Mcp->>Mcp: Validate MCP_API_KEY and tool scope
  Mcp->>Core: POST /internal/core/ask
  Core->>Core: Plan metric_query or knowledge_lookup
  Core->>Db: Read-only query or vector retrieval
  Db-->>Core: Data and evidence
  Core-->>Mcp: Answer, artifacts, citations, trace_id
  Mcp-->>Client: MCP tool result
